# Graphite Crucible Market Size: Forecast & Trends 2026–2033

## Introduction
Graphite crucibles are high-temperature resistant containers used for melting, refining, and alloying metals.
They offer excellent thermal conductivity, chemical stability, and resistance to thermal shock, making them
essential in metallurgy, electronics, aerospace, and precious metal processing industries.

