## Market Trends

### Technological Advancements in Graphite Materials
Manufacturers are improving graphite purity, density, and oxidation resistance to enhance crucible lifespan
and operational efficiency.

### Increasing Adoption in High-Temperature Applications
High-density and ultra-high-density graphite crucibles are increasingly used in aerospace alloys and specialty
metal processing applications.

### Sustainability and Energy Efficiency
Graphite crucibles support energy-efficient melting processes due to faster heat transfer and lower fuel
consumption.

